defaultThe Royal Town Planning Institute (RTPI) has over 23,000 members who work in the public, private, v
defaultoluntary and education sectors.
default It is a charity 
defaultwhose
default purpose
default is
default to develop the art and science of town planning for the benefit of the public. 
defaultT
defaulthe RTPI develops and shapes policy affecting the built environment, works to raise professional standards and supports members through continu
defaultous education, practice advice, training and development.
