defaultUp and down the country planners are working on the creation of rou
defaultnded communities 
defaulttogether 
defaultwith the homes, 
defaultjobs 
defaultand facilities 
defaultthey need. The centralisation of most investment decisions by the public sector and regulated industries causes delay and 
defaultmakes it harder to deliver 
defaultplans to 
defaultshape and 
defaultimprove individual places.
