defaultThe right public services 
default(and other functions, including 
defaultpolicy making
default) 
defaultshould be delivered at the right level.  There is substanti
defaultal sco
defaultpe for devolution of services c
defaulturrently administered by Whitehall; however a subregional level is not necessarily the only level to which they might be devolved.  Individual local authorities may also be suitable
default, as indeed may areas larger than subr
defaultegions, depending on the function
